{"tha-ap99:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap99:0.2":"Sudhavagga ","tha-ap99:0.3":"Madhupindikattheraapadana ","tha-ap99:1.1":"“Vipine kanane disva, ","tha-ap99:1.2":"appasadde nirakule; ","tha-ap99:1.3":"Siddhattham isinam settham, ","tha-ap99:1.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap99:2.1":"Nibbutattam mahanagam, ","tha-ap99:2.2":"nisabhajaniyam yatha; ","tha-ap99:2.3":"Osadhimva virocantam, ","tha-ap99:2.4":"devasanghanamassitam. ","tha-ap99:3.1":"Vitti mamahu tavade, ","tha-ap99:3.2":"nanam uppajji tavade; ","tha-ap99:3.3":"Vutthitassa samadhimha, ","tha-ap99:3.4":"madhum datvana satthuno. ","tha-ap99:4.1":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap99:4.2":"pakkamim pacinamukho; ","tha-ap99:4.3":"Catuttimsamhi kappamhi, ","tha-ap99:4.4":"raja asim sudassano. ","tha-ap99:5.1":"Madhu bhisehi savati, ","tha-ap99:5.2":"bhojanamhi ca tavade; ","tha-ap99:5.3":"Madhuvassam pavassittha, ","tha-ap99:5.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap99:6.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap99:6.2":"yam madhum adadim tada; ","tha-ap99:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap99:6.4":"madhudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap99:7.1":"Catuttimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap99:7.2":"cattaro te sudassana; ","tha-ap99:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap99:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap99:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap99:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap99:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap99:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma madhupindiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap99:10.1":"Madhupindikattherassapadanam sattamam. "}